<div>Check LHS = RHS</div>

<div>Evaluate \(\dfrac{3}{4}a - \dfrac{1}{3}\) if \(a=\dfrac{14}{3}\)</div>

\[
\begin{align*}
&= \dfrac{3}{4}\left(\dfrac{14}{3}\right) - \dfrac{1}{3} \\
&= \dfrac{7}{2} - \dfrac{1}{3} \\
&= \dfrac{19}{6}
\end{align*}
\]

<div>Evaluate \(\dfrac{1}{2}a + \dfrac{5}{6}\) if \(a=\dfrac{14}{3}\)</div>

\[
\begin{align*}
&= \dfrac{1}{2}\left(\dfrac{14}{3}\right) + \dfrac{5}{6} \\
&= \dfrac{7}{3} + \dfrac{5}{6} \\
&= \dfrac{19}{6}
\end{align*}
\]
